title: This Streamer Just Ruined His Life Forever...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a Kick streamer known as Johnny Somali who recently has been IRL streaming in Japan, with so many flagrant violations he's now become a target of spectacle for the legal system and may face serious prison time for being such a public nuisance. Thanks for watching!
